  <h1>Free SEO & GEO Crawler</h1>
  <p>A comprehensive, open-source SEO and AI search (GEO) auditing tool. Analyze any website for 130+ checks across technical SEO, on-page optimization, performance, security, structured data, and generative engine optimization.</p>

  <div class="docs-screenshot">
    <img src="/screenshots/home.png" alt="Booltools Seo Crawler — Home page" loading="lazy" />
    <p class="docs-caption">Home page — enter a domain, pick a rule preset, and start analyzing.</p>
  </div>

  <h2>Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>130+ audit rules</strong> covering 15 categories</li>
    <li><strong>GEO (Generative Engine Optimization)</strong> checks for AI search readiness</li>
    <li><strong>Real-time progress</strong> with Server-Sent Events during analysis</li>
    <li><strong>Rule presets</strong> — Blog, E-Commerce, Video, Landing Page, Technical-only, GEO-only, and more</li>
    <li><strong>Customizable rules</strong> — select/deselect individual rules before analysis</li>
    <li><strong>Export reports</strong> as CSV or Markdown (including AI-agent-friendly format)</li>
    <li><strong>CI/CD SDK</strong> — run SEO checks in your deployment pipeline</li>
    <li><strong>Localhost crawling</strong> — test your development server before deploying</li>
    <li><strong>Sitemap analysis</strong> — validates all URLs in your sitemap, detects orphan pages</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Audit Report</h2>
  <p>After analysis, you get a detailed report with issues grouped by category, severity indicators, and actionable fix recommendations.</p>
  <div class="docs-screenshot">
    <img src="/screenshots/report.png" alt="Audit report with SEO and GEO scores" loading="lazy" />
    <p class="docs-caption">Audit report — scores, issues by category, affected URLs, and export options.</p>
  </div>

